reviewText: The dvd worked very well and both storys are good. The Stranger is a well done drama, and Along Came Jones is a nice little comedy.

Very good and very happy with product.  I'm so happy that there are two movies in the package.  I like Loretta Young
especially these two movies

I had seen this film in the 1940's and remembered one of the few westerns
Where the hero was useless with a gun.it greatly appealed to me and Gary Cooper
Was my favourite cowboy anyway.
